fields.subtitle: Join millions who use Plastiq to pay vendors with a credit card. Pay for inventory, advertising, shipping, rent and more with your Brex card. You’ll also benefit from a discounted 2% Plastiq fee on the first $200,000 you spend.
fields.footnote: Signing up will not affect your credit score. After the first $200,000 of payments through Plastiq via your Brex card, the Plastiq fee will become 2.35% for ongoing transactions made via your Brex card.
